00559a651a16d600cc5b293c8376d1e5038d994bb58de5a4a2a8cb2fe8b620d1dc0789f4157d0cb64203b0bd7d6402a872d5ef23d9a54d243221907c34545f0a  0001-rockchip-Add-initial-support-for-the-PinePhone-Pro.patch
